Semantic grep that stays local

Usage: ivygrep [OPTIONS] [QUERY] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  index   
  add     
  rm      
  status  
  daemon  
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Arguments:
  [QUERY]  

Options:
  -f, --force               
      --regex               
      --json                
  -C, --context <CONTEXT>   [default: 0]
      --type <TYPE_FILTER>  
  -n, --limit <LIMIT>       
      --no-watch            
  -h, --help                Print help
  -V, --version             Print version
